  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK349">
<l>paṟṟaṟṟa kaṇṇē piṟappaṟukkum maṟṟu</l>
<l>nilaiyāmai kāṇap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>At the moment in which desire has been abandoned, (other) births will be cut off; when that has not been done, instability will be seen.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
